{"tid":1534582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解速龍同班狗打人果陣班on9大愛左膠又唔拉住佢地？","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:30:42.000Z","uid":159473,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"163d553e11cb33196e9e0ce0df4832bf6d2a4675","tid":1534582,"uid":159473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"速龍同班狗打人果陣班左膠去撚咗邊？班大愛左膠唔係好鐘意拉撚住人叫人唔好打？當示威者好恰係咪？下次邊個阻撚住打撚埋佢。"},{"pid":"8dd4d9ce357548469ea51a68282171c0fa35a3da","tid":1534582,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"947537959f8593e8a888fcf60ad5e833e294dcc0","tid":1534582,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"7e5b17d9cd69510e39332ee20c404a2007891dfe","tid":1534582,"uid":63757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"真正既「欺善怕惡」"},{"pid":"1a1ee81b60442d44feb41d4c4e6aeed00ae23d78","tid":1534582,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"因為佢地已經走咗"},{"pid":"543bc5c4d3b32937c5405f5fc7e10d16be5151d9","tid":1534582,"uid":32325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"因為佢地考慮嘅係邊個<span style=\"color: red;\">拉得住</span><br />\n而唔係邊個<span style=\"color: red;\">應該要拉住</span>"}]}